historial.content: I spoke with Timmy. She said she'll be able to pay after payday, next Friday (the 12th). I put her in pending status.
PT called. He was worried about the message about the insurance not covering his HST after Dec 31st. Explained him insurance may change the plan and deductible at the end of the year.
PT called requesting us to send to the doctor the HST results. Results refaxed.
